Ultima Weapons

Who can Use Ultima Weapons

Ultima weapons are powerful arms—one for each weapon type—that may be equipped by allies who have been enhanced to crystal strength level 90.


*Tap and hold on an ultima weapon in the Cast or Sublimate menus to view the weapon's details.


Casting Ultima Weapons

Ultima weapons can be obtained with the Cast/Sublimate option on the Enhancements screen.

Casting an ultima weapon requires a specialized material called providence cores.

Possessing two ultima weapons of the same type will allow two allies in the party to equip one each, but subsequent castings will require more providence cores than were needed for the first casting.


Sublimating Ultima Weapons

After casting an ultima weapon, more providence cores can be used to further enhance it through sublimation.

Each ultima weapon may be sublimated up to five times.

Providence cores needed for casting and sublimating ultima weapons may be obtained as:
・Ultima mission rewards
・Additional premium mission rewards available after purchasing a Premium Moogle Pass

Refer to the following game guides for more details on each method of obtaining providence cores.
